{"tid":2113661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中8戰機現身南海永興島　美B1B轟炸機增兵關島","createTime":"2020-07-18T09:29:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-18T10:03:37.000Z","uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ea08090be5fec17fb9b4fb31ee0ba8af21a2e879","tid":2113661,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T09:29:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200718/photo/bkn-20200718150544056-0718_00952_001_01p.jpg?20200718154923\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20200718%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200718150544056-0718_00952_001_01p.jpg%3F20200718154923&h=6256ae7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n衞星圖片拍到解放軍戰機出現在永興島機場的停機坪。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國兩艘航空母艦再入南海演習後，衞星圖片拍到在西沙群島永興島機場，停機坪出現8架解放軍戰機，數量更是歷次發現最多。與此同時，美軍向南海外圍的西太平洋戰略重地關島，由本土調派多2架B1B轟炸機，令當地的轟炸機數量增至4架。<br />\n<br />\n美國傳媒周五（17日）報道，根據Planet Labs當天拍攝的衞星圖片，在永興島機場的停機坪上，出現4架疑為殲11B的戰機，以及4架相信是殲轟7的戰機。4架殲11B周三（15日）已現身該機場，但翌日不在同一位置，直至周五、即美軍在南海展開「雙航母」行動當天才再度現身，而解放軍本月1日至5日曾在西沙群島舉行演習。<br />\n<br />\n另外，追蹤軍機動向的社交網帳戶Golf9周六（18日）表示，美國空軍2架B1B轟炸機從本土出發，並取道太平洋中部，經夏威夷上空前往關島安德森空軍基地。美國太平洋空軍前一天宣布這款轟炸機重返印太地區，屬於轟炸機特遣隊行動，並執行戰略威懾任務，加強區內以規則為基礎的國際秩序，展示美方對集體防禦的承諾。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200718/photo/bkn-20200718150544056-0718_00952_001_03p.jpg?20200718154923\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20200718%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200718150544056-0718_00952_001_03p.jpg%3F20200718154923&h=bb6d6270&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美軍B1B轟炸機再次部署關島<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200718/photo/bkn-20200718150544056-0718_00952_001_02p.jpg?20200718154923\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20200718%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200718150544056-0718_00952_001_02p.jpg%3F20200718154923&h=3a480757&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nGolf9提供美軍B1B轟炸機前往關島的飛行路線圖<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200718/bkn-20200718150544056-0718_00952_001.html</code></pre>"},{"pid":"27459ea6560bdcf7f03d4729929fc72b2e393788","tid":2113661,"uid":259088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T09:29:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"79b0f3880615f900a6e99acb28b241eb288ba923","tid":2113661,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T09:29:55.000Z","msg":"開戰未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd09a25cb1bdef4e1c58b4f991aea9fada4ac5e9","tid":2113661,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T09:30:36.000Z","msg":"出B2未？"},{"pid":"07280ab7009cd76ed1d55984fe101ce6684b6f7a","tid":2113661,"uid":20563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T09:30:50.000Z","msg":"8 架 ....<br />\n人地一隻航母 90架 ....而家2隻航母"},{"pid":"f87027abcce18cb82613c76ca5120faf04e2ed5c","tid":2113661,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T09:31:37.000Z","msg":"島都炸到佢陸沉"},{"pid":"45c776f88643ffc729060f1a09539212191a2d3d","tid":2113661,"uid":333163,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T09:32:23.000Z","msg":"大陸响南海填人工島其實係咪想學美國咁環球駐軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db4f91538cf97d8e5f0128e18a31b6e80efc4bed","tid":2113661,"uid":3480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"07280ab7009cd76ed1d55984fe101ce6684b6f7a","tid":2113661,"uid":20563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T09:30:50.000Z","msg":"8 架 ....<br />\n人地一隻航母 90架 ....而家2隻航母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T09:34:31.000Z","msg":"飛得郁嘅應該飛哂過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\